OL,4,CSchools want 75% rebate on this
OL,5,Csummer's exam fees
OL,6, School and college leaders in England
OL,7, want a rebate of at least 75% on this
OL,8, year's exam fees, a survey has found.
OL,10,FThis year's GCSE and A-level results
OL,11,Fwill be decided by teachers, after
OL,12,Fsummer exams were cancelled in January
OL,13,Fbecause of the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,15,FNearly two in three (65%) head teachers
OL,16,Fsurveyed by the Association of School
OL,17,Fand College Leaders said exam boards
OL,18,Fshould offer a 75% rebate this year.
OL,20,FBoards say they still need to cover
OL,21,Fcosts but will pass on any savings.
